1.The goal of the game is to destroy all colored bricks on each map.
2.To move the bar use the A/D keys.
3.The ' '(space bar) is used to pause/resume the game.
4.To get a bonus destroy a green brick and catch the afferent bonus.
5.The yellow triangle bonus gives you 3 laser shots.
  Use 'W' to fire the laser.
6.The read heart bonus gives you one extra life.
7.The blue bonus expands the bar.


